metadata.name: That One Special Moment
metadata.description: I usually capture what hook my eyes, never hesitated in that. Once i saw this image which hooked me, not my eyes but my heart. for the first time i failed to click at the moment. i stood there for a minute or so and felt the view. but i was not able to stop my hand from capturing it. got it easily, this time not with my eyes, but with my heart.
